# Master resume bullets

When adding or editing bullet `text` in `master/experience/` or `master/projects/`, read and follow **[`Resume Bullets.md`](../../Resume%20Bullets.md)** (Google X–Y–Z, 20–40 words, one accomplishment per bullet).

Also apply that guide when [`New Job Project.md`](../../New%20Job%20Project.md) or [`New Job Listing.md`](../../New%20Job%20Listing.md) workflows create or suggest new master bullets.
